competitive cascades to\n\"inform\" and \"heal\" aggressors. We show that IC and LT models can be used in\naggression minimization, providing less intrusive alternatives to the blocking\ntechniques currently employed by popular online social network platforms.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 May 2020 13:41:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 22 May 2020 10:18:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 1 Sep 2020 10:29:33 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 23 Dec 2020 10:45:44 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Mon, 30 Aug 2021 11:36:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-31"}
